      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "I figure that every answer here will require some test setup, execution of the method to test, and then assert the properties. There&#39;s no real overhead to my answer from what I can see, only that I have two assertions on seaprate lines so that a failed assertion can clearly identify what value is missing."
