      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "It would be best to also include a message within assertTrue so that the error message is more intelligible. Without a message, if it fails, JUnit will just throw a AssertionFailedError without any error message. So best to include something like &quot;results should contain new MyItem(\\&quot;foo\\&quot;)&quot;."
