    "body" : "<p><a href=\"https://assertj.github.io/doc/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Assertj</a> is good at this.</p>\n<pre><code>import static org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat;\n\n    assertThat(myClass.getMyItems()).extracting(&quot;name&quot;).contains(&quot;foo&quot;, &quot;bar&quot;);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Big plus for assertj compared to hamcrest is easy use of code completion.</p>\n"
